Interfaces: Twitter, IM, E-Mail, Web

Commands:
  # !join [profiles]
  !update [profiles]
  !remove [profiles]
  !set role:[member|speaker|visitor|...] (default: member)
  !set status:[away|...]

Sources:
  me:[url]
  github:[handle]
  twitter:[handle]
  ...


Twitter Bot on Heroku
  POST to /ping
  check twitter timeline for unprocessed replies since last ping - 1 min
  process tweets
  store processed tweet ids
  store ping timestamp


@rugb !update         # add my identity
@rugb !join           # join the group @rugb
@rugb !visit          # visit

@rugb !add svenfuchs  # add someone else